BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:pl-12306748142@voicesprofessionallearning
DTSTAMP:20260722T131135Z
DTSTART:20260730T160000Z
DTEND:20260730T223000Z
SUMMARY:Guided E-LOP Planning
LOCATION:Voices College-Bound Language Academy\, Hellyer Avenue\, San Jose\, CA\, USA
DESCRIPTION:Pre-work: All BMs and Nancy check Kristen's ELOP Monday Board to see what tasks are missing or need to be added. \n\nInplay Training (from Kristen or platform people?) on new ELOP/attendance recovery platform with ELOP directors from Boys & Girls Club/Faces  + all BMs + Nancy\n\nSite Breakout groups with ELOP directors + BMs to talk about this year's logistics\, room assignments\, communication alignment & needs\n\nBring your own lunch or grab lunch (ELOP directors dismissed)\n\n\n\nELOP Monday Project Alignment & Date Setting - Kristen\, Nancy + BMS\, aligning on all ELOP Monday board tasks and due dates for the whole year (enrichment\, summer school\, science camp\, and whatever else)\n\nPost work: BMs & Nancy have a week to go back to their sites to make sure they can attend to this collective date-setting calendar.
END:VEVENT
